            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1681376939528-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Thread the <strong>spiced tofu</strong> onto the <strong>soaked skewers</strong></p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once very hot, add the <strong>tofu skewers</strong> and cook for 5-6 min, turning occasionally until golden – these are you <strong>tofu souvlaki skewers</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1681376943526-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1681376943526-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1681376943526-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1681376943526-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1681376943526-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, roughly chop your<strong> tomato[es]</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and roughly shred</p><p>Add the<strong> shredded lettuce </strong>and<strong> chopped tomato </strong>to a bowl with the <strong>pickled shallot liquid </strong>and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>– this is your <strong>dressed salad</strong></p><p>Add your<strong> wholemeal pittas </strong>to a baking tray and put the tray in the oven for 3-4 min or until warmed through</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1681376947159-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1681376947159-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1681376947159-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1681376947159-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1681376947159-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top the <strong>tofu souvlaki skewers </strong>with the <strong>pickled shallots</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>herby fries</strong>, <strong>dressed salad</strong>, <strong>warmed pitta </strong>and <strong>garlic mayo </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
